NAME
     9x more scummy and rat infested than rio. Just say NEIN.

SYNOPSIS
     9x [-v]

DESCRIPTION
     9x is a sucky X11 window manager and scummy rio rip-off.  It provides far
     more than you bargained for.  Do 9 things and do them poorly.

OPTIONS
     -v  Erase computer. Weep.

MOUSE
   Desktop & Bar
     Button 1  Window menu.

     Button 2  Desktop menu.

     Button 3  Sweep new terminal.

     Scroll    Cycle desktops.

   Window Menu
     Button 1  Focus.

     Button 2  Delete.

     Button 3  Sweep.

   Window Borders
     Button 1  Resize.

     Button 2  Delete.

     Button 3  Move.

     B1 + B3   Maximize.

KEYBOARD
     Alt+Space         Launch.

     Alt+Tab           Cycle windows.

     Alt+Shift+Tab     Reverse cycle windows.

     Alt+F4            Delete.

     Alt+F10           Maximize.

     Alt+F11           Fullscreen.

     Alt+[1..9]        Desktop 1-9.

     Alt+Shift+[1..9]  Window to desktop 1-9.

LAUNCHER
     Return     Launch.

     Tab        Complete.

     Backspace  Delete.

     Down       Next.

     Up         Previous.

     Escape     Cancel.

CUSTOMIZATION
     Read the goddamn src(1) you filthy heathen.

BUGS
     Programs that depend on EWMH/ICCCM may shit the bed.

     Cursed cursors & Caerbannog bunnies lurking in dark corners...
